Educated to PhD level with 10+ yearsâ€™ experience of industrial medicinal chemistry 
Highly motivated with a track record of candidate delivery 
Embrace modern drug discovery technologies and enthusiasm to apply algorithm-derived compound designs 
Working proficiency and communication skills in verbal and written English 
